Biography

GENERAL: Chose to attend The College of Saint Rose because of the size and location of campus…Named his parents as the most influential people in his life…Enjoys hanging out with friends and working out…Listed Friends as a favorite TV show and Moneyball as a favorite movie…Admires Clayton Kershaw as an athlete…Son of Maria and Peter Stewart.

HIGH SCHOOL: Played club with the South Troy Dodgers…Helped the Brothers win the Section II Championship in baseball…Also playing basketball and volleyball.
